# 6. Implementation, Experimental Results and Test Cases

## 6.1 Implementation Details

### 6.1.1 Frontend Implementation

The React frontend is organized as follows:

**Entry Point:** `main.jsx` initializes the React application with `BrowserRouter` wrapping and renders the root `App` component.

**Routing:** `App.jsx` configures fourteen page-level routes using React Router DOM, with authentication-guarded routes based on user role. The `AuthContext` provider wraps the entire application, managing JWT token persistence, user state, and role-based access control.

**Key Page Components:**

| Component File | Size | Role | Key Functionality |
|---------------|------|------|-------------------|
| `Dashboard.jsx` | 23 KB | Patient | Health overview, recent appointments, AI reports, quick actions |
| `DoctorDashboard.jsx` | 36 KB | Doctor | Patient queue, appointments, prescription/report creation, co-pilot chatbot |
| `SuperAdminDashboard.jsx` | 39 KB | Admin | Platform analytics, user/order/appointment management, audit logs |
| `XRayScanner.jsx` | 30 KB | Patient | Image upload, clinical data form, AI inference invocation, triage results display |
| `PatientChatPortal.jsx` | 17 KB | Patient | Graph-RAG chat interface, PDF upload for ingestion, chat history sidebar |
| `Pharmacy.jsx` | 23 KB | Patient | Medicine catalog browsing, search, filtering |
| `CartPage.jsx` | 18 KB | Patient | Cart management, checkout, Razorpay payment |
| `LabTests.jsx` | 31 KB | Patient | Lab test catalog, scheduling, result viewing |
| `LandingPage.jsx` | 6 KB | Public | Marketing landing page |
| `HealthHiveLanding.jsx` | 23 KB | Public | Feature-rich landing with pricing section |

**Key Reusable Components:**

| Component | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `AuthCard.jsx` | Registration/login form with Google OAuth |
| `PrescriptionModal.jsx` | Multi-step prescription builder with signature capture |
| `PrescriptionViewer.jsx` | Formatted prescription display with PDF export |
| `ClinicalReportBuilder.jsx` | SOAP-format clinical report editor |
| `ClinicalReportViewer.jsx` | Formatted clinical report display |
| `MedicalChatbot.jsx` | Doctor co-pilot chatbot UI |
| `DoctorList.jsx` | Doctor selection grid with booking interface |
