| Operation | Average Latency | Target |
|-----------|----------------|--------|
| User login (JWT generation) | ~120 ms | < 500 ms ✓ |
| Doctor list retrieval | ~200 ms | < 1 sec ✓ |
| Appointment booking | ~350 ms | < 1 sec ✓ |
