### 6.2.6 Graph-RAG Retrieval Quality

The vector similarity search with a 0.70 cosine threshold demonstrates effective relevance filtering:

| Query Type | Relevant Docs in Graph | Retrieved (≥0.70) | Irrelevant Retrieved | Precision |
|-----------|----------------------|-------------------|---------------------|-----------|
| Condition-specific ("my diabetes medication") | 3 | 3 | 0 | 100% |
| Symptom-based ("chest pain history") | 2 | 2 | 0 | 100% |
| Lifestyle ("can I eat spicy food") | 1 | 1 | 0 | 100% |
| Unrelated ("weather today") | 0 | 0 | 0 | N/A (correctly returned empty) |

